{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "0a43777d-ae9f-4cd0-962d-d252b7e6525b",
    "name": "Corium Ludo API",
    "description": "API collection for Corium Ludo. Base URL: http://localhost:13000/corium/ludo/api\n\nFlow:\n1) Login as MR to get a Bearer token. ONLY MRs can create task entries; AM/RM/ZM get a 403 if they try.\n2) MR creates a task entry and uploads document IMAGES only (multipart 'documents'). Non-image formats are rejected with a 400 error.\n   - Task 1 (Doctor Conversions): num_prescriptions & num_pob both OPTIONAL. Any number of images. Approval = FLAT 6 points.\n   - Task 2 (POB): EXACTLY 1 image, num_pob (units) required > 0. Points = floor(num_pob/5)*2, computed on the fly (no total_points column).\n   - Task 3 (Combo POB): EXACTLY 1 image, doctor_name & pcode both REQUIRED.\n   - Task 4 (Live Prescriptions): images MUST equal num_prescriptions. 2 points per approved image.\n   - Task 5 (JCC): any images.\n3) The MR's AM/RM/ZM (organogram hierarchy: AM->MR, RM->AM+MR, ZM->RM+AM+MR) lists pending documents and bulk approves.\n4) MRs are NOT allowed to approve (403).\n\nTask keys: doctor_conversions, pob, combo_pob, live_prescriptions, jcc_conversion",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "5599247",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/5599247-0a43777d-ae9f-4cd0-962d-d252b7e6525b?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
